        <Icon name="questions/folder" class="text-6xl text-white" />
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-700">
        What kind of projects do you work on?
      </h3>
      <p>
        I commonly collaborate with startups on SaaS projects, but I have participated in various types of projects; the only limit is imagination.
      </p>
      <div></div>
